• Coordinate cost control;
• Analyze project-related financial data;
• Design, implement, and continuously improve financial management processes;
• Participate in financial systems development initiatives;
• Manage and develop human resources and employee relations;
• Assist the HR team in improving recruitment and employee development processes;
• Implement and monitor client communication strategies.
